score: part 1 of 5
&1
This note is for those using these files for creating sound files.
The last half of m.99 is displayed correctly but technically there
should be a quarter note irest on beat 4 so the sound would not
carry over into the last beat, but the mskpage program would not
accept an irest value of a quarter in col, 8.  In measure 26 there
is a similar but simpler situation but the mskpage program worked.
&1
