The above note is a quarter note in Roger, but in order to
display it properly in our system it was given a note value
of a half note in col. 8.  Technically there should be an
irest for a quarter note at the end of this measure but it
would not be accepted by the mskpage program.  There is a
similar but simpler situation in M.26 where mskpage worked.
